window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Kane is a six-foot-seven French Canadian. But, a year ago, he was a wolf.</b></p> <p>He'd been in the woods when a crazed, infected man attacked him. The next day, he transformed into a human.</p> <p>Now, Kane is searching for the Biting Man to get the answers he needs to become a wolf again and return to his pack.</p> <p>The only one who knows Kane's secret is a troubled young woman named Emelda. She needed out of a terrible situation; Kane needed someone who could drive. Wolves who become humans are terrible drivers.</p> <p>He also has a problem with moonlight. It changes Kane, but Emelda has only seen him turn into dogs. Usually, rather tiny ones. However, there is one transformation she has yet to see—the wolfwere.</p> <p>But Kane isn't the only one the man attacked. And while an infected wolf turned human, the people he bit became something else. Something horrible.</p> <p>Before they can get answers from the Biting Man, Emelda and Kane need to first take down the monsters he created.</p>"; 
